    <p><CtaButton href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0D2MF7R3C/ref=nosim?tag=coffee-site-20" external>Check price on Amazon</CtaButton></p>
    <p><strong>Why it wins this slot:</strong> It is one of the few truly compact machines that still offers full espresso + milk functionality.</p>

    <h3>5) Flair Neo Flex — Best Manual Espresso Value</h3>
    <ProductCard
      title="Flair Neo Flex"
      image={{ src: 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/61MqQwolqRL._AC_SL500_.jpg', alt: 'Flair Neo Flex manual espresso maker', width: 500, height: 500 }}
